Well [inaudible] to know.

00:02:58.445 --> 00:02:59.647 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Beautiful
heart and genius and--

00:02:59.647 --> 00:03:00.714 align:middle line:90%
>> AP: He's a wonderful guy.

00:03:00.714 --> 00:03:02.149 align:middle line:90%
