which will be the evidence

00:03:11.358 --> 00:03:13.794 align:middle line:84%
for consciousness existing
outside of the brain.

00:03:13.794 --> 00:03:16.764 align:middle line:84%
I'm writing one side of the book
and Ervin is writing the other.

00:03:16.764 --> 00:03:19.366 align:middle line:84%
And that will be published
probably about 18 months' time

00:03:19.366 --> 00:03:21.402 align:middle line:84%
by Inner Traditions
in the states.

00:03:21.402 --> 00:03:25.906 align:middle line:84%
But on top of that, I just
finished writing a biography

00:03:25.906 --> 00:03:28.942 align:middle line:84%
